# handlers — instead of, after, second-noun filter

verb tap
    * noun
    "Nothing to tap."

verb tap with
    * noun 'with' held
    "Nothing to tap with that."

room Room "A room."

    object stick "A stick."

    object drum "A drum."
        instead of tap with stick:
            say "Crack."
        instead of tap:
            say "Thud."
        after take:
            say "Groovy sound."

test "default"
    tap drum. "Thud"
    take stick.
    tap drum with stick. "Crack"
    take drum. "Groovy"
